@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Lifecycle Statechart

[*] --> Constructed

Constructed --> Prepared : prepareToPlay()
Prepared --> Active : first processBlock()
Active --> Active : processBlock()
Active --> Suspended : host suspend / setActive(false)
Suspended --> Active : host resume / setActive(true)
Prepared --> Released : releaseResources()
Active --> Released : releaseResources()
Suspended --> Released : releaseResources()
Released --> Prepared : prepareToPlay()

Prepared --> ErrorBypass : invalid config
Active --> ErrorBypass : non-finite parameter\nor DSP invariant failure
ErrorBypass --> Prepared : reset with valid config
ErrorBypass --> Released : releaseResources()

Released --> [*]

state Active {
  [*] --> RealtimeProcessing
  RealtimeProcessing --> RealtimeProcessing : processBlock within CPU budget
}

note right of ErrorBypass
ErrorBypass must be bounded:
no throw through host callback,
no blocking recovery in audio thread.
end note

@enduml

